{"type": "article", "id": 35935, "title": "意大利版《Vogue》主编逝世，以及，英国设计师把Nike鞋做成了emoji | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2016-12-23T03:05:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 442, "name": "HUMAN MADE"}, {"id": 955, "name": "VOGUE"}, {"id": 9350, "name": "风衣"}, {"id": 14461, "name": "劳力士"}, {"id": 36102, "name": "如意"}, {"id": 11247, "name": "Franca Sozzani"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161223102906iSzOB9ZTrjGwkf2R.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/media/franca-sozzani-dead-10732792/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>意大利版《Vogue》的主编 Franca Sozzani 去世，享年 66 岁</b></a> | 周四，Franca Sozzani 于意大利米兰因肺癌逝世，享年 66 岁。Franca Sozzani 在 1988 年成为意大利《Vogue》的主编，她让这本杂志成为所有的《Vogue》里最具有争议性的一个版本。今年九月，她的儿子，时尚摄影师 Francesco Carrozzini 花了四年为她拍摄的纪录片，在威尼斯电影节上首映。</p><p><a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2016-12-21/ruyi-group-said-to-plan-purchase-of-trench-coat-maker-aquascutum\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>如意集团拟收购英国经典风衣品牌 Aquascutum</b></a> | Aquascutum 品牌于 1852 年创立，该品牌最初以军用品起步，后来也成为时尚界的潮流。2012 年，香港 YGM 贸易公司收购了 Aquascutum。日前传出山东如意集团拟斥资 1.2 亿元收购 Aquascutum 的消息。在今年早些时候，如意集团曾从私募基金KKR 手中收购了法国时尚集团 SMCP。&nbsp;</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>巴黎时尚店铺 colette 与 Mad Paris 携手，创作了名为<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/colette-x-mad-paris-x-rolex-milgauss-who-cares\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Who Cares 的劳力士 Milgauss 定制表款</a>。这款手表保留了劳力士的经典不锈钢表带和表盘。其白色的表面加入了 colette 标志性蓝色调的 Who cares, I’m already late 字样。这款定制手表限量 5 枚，售价为 18200 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223100042DPpM49v60HS8uahg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223100042pYQavSmCubMBg9h6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>为 2018 冬季奥运会预热，<a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/nike-cortez-metallic-pack\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nike Cortez 推出了全新金属配色版本</a>，分别代表奥运奖牌的金、银、铜配色，定价为 69 欧元。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016122309595803bXaxyPDJKUNruz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666923\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223100017qhzfwntm58OMxbNj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223100024vwDY0upRZAIeH8i6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667163\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223100024cSOi1DmA7L0MaQlU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666412\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>圣诞送礼物的话，不妨试试这款<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2016/12/23/modular-3d-printed-chocolates/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> 3D 打印模块巧克力</a>。这个巧克力来自澳大利亚设计工作室 Universal Favourite，这些巧克力可以任意组合，每一块都有不同的口味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223095947aqid6I83b5PLmsKn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612230959470Y7f1tXMPu34nQGO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223095947Kcfb1CSij70FBkAQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223095948lOko5FcJRNYQydz3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223095948DN2LeWqmXvAy4bGZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223095948BmDYZbg2QNMKdaJA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://hypebeast.cn/2016/12/haven-x-human-made-decade-of-permanence\" rel=\"nofollow\">日本街头品牌 Human Made 为加拿大时尚名店 HAVEN 十周年店庆，发布了两款联名新作</a>。包括一件可以双面穿的刺绣夹克衫和一件印花 T-shirt，定价分别为 1118 美元和 82 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223095916jcE3KhQsZgAPb19H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223095928S4reXhYT3pBgIlLU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223095928aefQ1TuyAOk6s28M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223095929dA24VMjc3E18DTXy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223095929hwfQr8jxcaX5ulCZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612230959294bLrdtZB8WSCEHAc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667236\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>英国设计师 Chris Labrooy 擅长把现实事物进行夸张或扭曲化表达，他这次就<a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/art/chris-labrooy-nike-presto-ultra-flyknit-illustrations-12-21-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">把 Nike 的 Flyknit 鞋做成了 emoji </a>的样子，还挺有趣的。&nbsp;</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223095845SJPLNDcUOy4WHf0K.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223095854vsziDrXdMwButmHV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223095854igyZYFR1ITNBVu2z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223095854WKLT2dpPtZc53Cn7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161223095900HopQENRw9uIxSnmd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自：<a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/designer-luxury/the-fashion-world-remembers-franca-sozzani-10733131/\" rel=\"nofollow\">wwd</a><br></p>"}